{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/24.gif?t=1736369574\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Mithrall: A World Carved by Legend and Iron</h2>Enter the realm of Mithrall, an open-world MMO that fuses the freedom of sandbox crafting with the thrill of survival. Embark on a journey where the legacy of dwarves is in your hands, and every sunset could end in glory or peril.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><strong>Tranquil Beginnings:</strong> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/265.gif?t=1736369574\" /><br>Begin your saga within the peaceful confines of a dwarven city, a place where the rhythm of the anvil's beat is a testament to prosperity and calm.<br><br><strong>The Call of the Horizon:</strong> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/3.gif?t=1736369574\" /><br>Gaze upon the vast world that awaits, a canvas for your ambition, filled with distant mysteries shrouded in mist and guarded by dragons.<br><br><strong>Artisanal Mastery:</strong> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/1.gif?t=1736369574\" /><br>Ascend from humble beginnings to become a master of the forge, where every ingot smelted and sword tempered marks another step towards greatness.<br><br><strong>A Tapestry of Servers:</strong> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/2.gif?t=1736369574\" /><br>Explore the seamless integration of realms through server meshing technology, creating an uninterrupted continuum for thousands of concurrent souls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Season-Based World </h2>Witness the evolution of Mithrall with seasons that bring not only a renewed landscape but also new lore, events, and challenges that test the mettle of every dwarf.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Reputation is Everything</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/4-opti.gif?t=1736369574\" /><br>Your actions carry weight, forging your reputation across the lands. Will you be known as a daring explorer, a shrewd merchant, or a solitary wanderer? Your story, your renown.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Wilds Await</h2>Engage in a rich PVE experience, facing off against the creatures of myth and legend, mining the depths for riches, or discovering secrets lost to time.<br><br>Forge your destiny in the fires of Mithrall, where every strike of the hammer, every strategic alliance, and every battle waged is a verse in the song of your legend. Your journey commences now.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736369574","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/page.bg.jpg?t=1736369574","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736369574","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736369574","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838890/extras/24.gif?t=1736369574\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Mithrall: A World Carved by Legend and Iron</h2>Enter the realm of Mithrall, an open-world MMO that fuses the freedom of sandbox crafting with the thrill of survival. Embark o